                  <h5><a href="/web/20170202034942/http://www.newstatesman.com/politics/media/2017/01/watch-ken-clarke-s-blistering-anti-brexit-speech-article-50-debate">Watch: Ken Clarke’s blistering anti-Brexit speech in the Article 50 debate</a> </h5>
                </div>
           </div></li>
      </ul></div>    </div>
  
  
  
  
  
  
